      },
      "block_order": [
        "link_TbzrQr"
      ],
      "name": "t:sections.n_guide-content.name",
      "settings": {
        "use_own_file": true,
        "active": false,
        "must_read": false,
        "heading": "Usage Instructions",
        "text": "<h2>Usage Instructions</h2><p>The Faucet Filter can be installed in 2 minutes, with filter replacement needed just once every 3 months.</p><p><strong>How To Install:</strong></p><ol><li>Remove faucet aerator. Simply attach and twist it off using the key for removal.</li><li>Find the faucet thread accessory which best fits your faucet size.</li><li>Clip Qure Faucet Filter onto the faucet. Once you hear it click, it is installed. Turn the toggle button to “Q” mark on the filter and enjoy healthier, clearer skin!</li></ol>",
        "slides_per_view": ""
      }
    },
    "n_guide_content_kqaH3N": {
      "type": "n_guide-content",
      "name": "t:sections.n_guide-content.name",
      "settings": {
        "use_own_file": true,
        "active": false,
        "must_read": false,
        "heading": "Product Claims & User Study",
        "text": "<h2>Product Claims & User Study</h2><p>Key claims:</p><ul><li>Safe for sensitive, dry, and acne-prone skin.</li><li>Filtered water helps improve the performance of skincare products.</li><li>Clinically proven to boost hydration in just 4 weeks.</li><li>Reduces the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles with daily use.</li></ul><p>Results from a 4-week user study:</p><ul><li>80% reported reduced dryness after 4 weeks</li><li>77% said tightness after washing decreased</li><li>Many users saw better product absorption and improved glow</li></ul>",
        "slides_per_view": ""
      }
    },
    "n_guide_content_97j94F": {
      "type": "n_guide-content",
      "blocks": {
        "quote_eEhzyk": {
          "type": "quote",
          "settings": {
            "style": "blue",
            "text": "<p>Remember to <strong>add a personal touch</strong> to the messaging, talk about how the filter makes your skin feel.</p><p>Examples:</p><ul><li>“This filter changed my skin.”</li><li>“Since using this filter, my hair has never looked better!”</li></ul>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "quote_eEhzyk"
      ],
      "name": "t:sections.n_guide-content.name",
      "settings": {
        "use_own_file": true,
        "active": false,
        "must_read": true,
        "heading": "Content Requirements",
        "text": "<h2>Content Requirements</h2><p>Messaging must include:</p><ul><li>Tap water often contains irritants that affect skin health.</li><li>The Qure Filter helps remove them with no extra steps — just clearer water at the source.</li><li>Filtered water make your skincare work better.</li></ul>",
        "slides_per_view": ""
      }
    },
