      "name": "t:sections.n_guide-content.name",
      "settings": {
        "use_own_file": true,
        "active": false,
        "must_read": false,
        "heading": "Creative Direction",
        "text": "<h2>Creative Direction</h2><p>Recording Guidelines</p><ul><li>Use bright, natural lighting. No filters.</li><li>Please do not wear makeup (unless to show makeup removal).</li><li>Ensure the Qure Faucet filter is the main focus of the content.</li><li>Keep backgrounds clean and uncluttered.</li><li>In cover photos, always show the filter in use (unless agreed otherwise).</li></ul><p>Content Guidelines</p><ul><li>Please showcase the <strong>360° rotating nozzle</strong> in action.</li><li>Include shots of the filter installation.</li><li>Include shots of old dirty faucet accelerator when removing it.</li><li>If changing the filter, showcase the dirty old filter and compare with the new filter.</li></ul>",
        "slides_per_view": "2"
      }
    },
    "n_guide_content_6FT6Ci": {
      "type": "n_guide-content",
      "blocks": {
        "text_slider_K4LyR4": {
          "type": "text_slider",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>The Hidden Skin Dangers in Every Drop</strong></p><p>Highlight the unseen contaminants in tap water that negatively affect skin, positioning the Qure Faucet Filter as the solution to purer, skin-loving water.</p><p>[note_grey]<strong>Hook:</strong>\"Think your tap water is clean? Think again. Chlorine, heavy metals, and microplastics can hide in your water and harm your skin over time. The Qure Faucet Filter removes up to 99% of these impurities, giving your skin a clean slate every time you wash.\"[/note]</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_slider_cm9GmM": {
          "type": "text_slider",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Before & After Transformation</strong></p><p>Showcase a clear before-and-after transformation to emphasize the positive effects of filtered water on skin health. Focus on the visible results and the real impact the filter has had over time.</p><p>[note_grey]<strong>Hook:</strong>\"I’ve been using the Qure Faucet Filter for 2 months, and here’s the difference: This is my skin before (show redness/acne), and now (show glowy skin, no makeup). The change has been amazing, and I owe it all to purer water.\"[/note]</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_slider_CCUqjY": {
          "type": "text_slider",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>City Girl Struggle</strong></p><p>Target urban dwellers by sharing a relatable story of how city living impacted skin health, with the Qure Faucet Filter as the solution to improve it. Connect emotionally by sharing a personal struggle and transformation.</p><p>[note_grey]<strong>Hook:</strong>\"Can you believe this was how my skin looked when I first moved to the city? After using the Qure Faucet Filter, my skin is now clearer, smoother, and glowing. It’s crazy what the right water can do for you”.[/note]</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_slider_RAiRHD": {
          "type": "text_slider",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>The Skincare Secret You’ve Been Missing</strong></p><p>Unfiltered tap water can strip your skin, cause irritation, and prevent your skincare from working its best. Once I switched to Qure Faucet Filter, my skin calmed down, I got way less breakouts and my skin was more hydrated -  finally looking the way I wanted it to.</p><p>[note_grey]<strong>Hook:</strong>“Spending hundreds on skincare products but still not seeing results? I was too, until I realized the REAL problem wasn’t my products—it was the water I was using.”[/note]</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_slider_ymd9tD": {
          "type": "text_slider",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>The Worst Skincare Mistake</strong></p><p>Educate viewers about the common mistake of using unfiltered tap water for skincare. Position the Qure Faucet Filter as an easy and effective solution that is proven to improve skin health.</p><p>[note_grey]<strong>Hook:</strong>Friend 1: \"What’s the worst skincare mistake you see?\" / Friend 2: \"Washing your face with unfiltered tap water!\"[/note]</p>"
          }
        }
      },
